{"tid":1842882,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"武漢肺炎 - 預測林鄭柒婆之因果報應","createTime":"2020-01-26T03:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T04:45:21.000Z","uid":125976,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee998461c26e69b7723334b31e6cfb1930405856","tid":1842882,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:16:33.000Z","msg":"2019年12月7日至2020年2月3日 (立春前)<br />\n柒婆嘅乙木生火剋金<br />\n屬「金」嘅呼吸道、肺部疫症開始醞釀<br />\n柒婆無視新型冠狀病毒疫症<br />\n容許廝殺列車繼續抵港<br />\n開始自私嘅瑞士之旅<br />\n間接助長疫症蔓延到港 (生火剋金)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2月4日至4月3日 (立春後清明前)<br />\n戊己土輔助受傷嘅「金」氣<br />\n疫症因為天氣變暖得以舒緩<br />\n柒婆將正面結果歸功於佢嘅管治團隊嘅努力<br />\n最後得到土共讚揚，荒淫無道，天理不容<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4月4日至6月4日（清明後天安門事件前）<br />\n庚辛之氣報仇，反剋乙木嘅柒婆<br />\n<br />\n港人吉日吉時(柒婆受報)表<br />\n5月12日 9-11, 17-19時<br />\n5月22日 9-11, 17-19時<br />\n6月1日 9-11, 17-19時<br />\n<br />\n可應之事：<br />\n1. 受利器所傷<br />\n2. 神經、頸、肝、關節為主之病<br />\n3. 交通意外<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">祝願香港否極泰來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6c900327beeed33e5ec56a522895d5e83f8f6333","tid":1842882,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:16:49.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"e5cafd2952c0b64194731d41f352f9def1fa2b75","tid":1842882,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:22:55.000Z","msg":"流年乙庚合，柒婆難以用佢嘅比劫劏煞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864d97e32a7c0beb051727805d5f0ce80f35d966","tid":1842882,"uid":156076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:27:35.000Z","msg":"拉上去打靶啦<br />\n台灣單野直頭係叛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33ff6a05dcdaaf55341be728d77a6e8c6254bb8","tid":1842882,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"864d97e32a7c0beb051727805d5f0ce80f35d966","tid":1842882,"uid":156076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"